OL,3,CLollipop lady raises tens-of-thousands
OL,4,Cfor charity after losing mum and
OL,5,Cbrother
OL,7,FMair Jones, who has raised over
OL,8,F#100,000 for Hope House/Ty Gobaith and
OL,9,Fthe Scope charity is one of the
OL,10,Ffinalists in the Pride of Britain
OL,11,FRegional Fundraiser of the Year award.
OL,13,FMair lost her mother and brother to
OL,14,Fcancer.
OL,16,F"My brother was only 39 and my mother
OL,17,Fwas 60. I thought I can't do anything
OL,18,Ffor them anymore but I can help
OL,19,Fsomebody else.'
