OL,7,FShe said that in their honour they did
OL,8,Fthe Memory Walk in London but she
OL,9,Fwanted to help more local causes and
OL,10,Fone that became close to her heart was
OL,11,Fthe Hope House Children's Hospice.
OL,13,F'I have raised #53,000 for Ty Gobaith
OL,14,Fand over #46,000 for the Scope charity
OL,15,Fshop in Pwllheli.'
OL,17,FA lollipop lady and teaching
OL,18,Fassistant, Mair started by having open
OL,19,Fdays in her home on the Llyn
OL,20,FPeninsula, but they had to stop
OL,21,Fbecause of Covid.
