OL,3,CLollipop lady raises tens-of-thousands
OL,4,Cfor charity after losing mum and
OL,5,Cbrother
OL,7,FShe asked her husband if she could
OL,8,Fhave a little shed to put outside her
OL,9,Fhome and it became known as Cwt
OL,10,FGobaith, also known as Cwt Anti Mair.
OL,12,FIn fine weather Mair fills rails and
OL,13,Ftables of clothes on the road outside
OL,14,Fher home with the shed acting as a
OL,15,FAladdin's cave of home wear and toys.
OL,17,FThe Cwt also acts as a meeting place
OL,18,Ffor people to go along and have a chat.
