OL,3,CLollipop lady raises tens-of-thousands
OL,4,Cfor charity after losing mum and
OL,5,Cbrother
OL,7,F"I have phone calls and texts from
OL,8,Fpeople saying they are feeling down
OL,9,Fand if the shed was open. They come
OL,10,Fhere and have a chat with everyone
OL,11,Felse who is here. I remember one
OL,12,Fperson stayed for three hours.
OL,14,F"I want everything to go for #1
OL,15,Fbecause a lot of people are
OL,16,Fstruggling. People don't have a lot of
OL,17,Fmoney to buy clothes, especially
OL,18,Fchildrens clothes. Everything is quite
OL,19,Fexpensive these days. So I do hope I
OL,20,Fam helping a lot of people.
